    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Duplicate of #11885?\r\n\r\nNo. #11885 is about that visible 1-tick stop at the end of an L-turn transitioning to straight movement. This issue is about (optionally) considering the Turn activity as IMove.IsMoving. L-turns don't use the Turn activity, so these are separate issues."
